privacy-passwords-finally-most-websites = Finally, most web sites let you recover your password if you’ve forgotten it. Usually these systems make you answer some “security questions” before you can reset your password. <strong>The answers to these questions need to be just as secret as your password.</strong> Otherwise, an attacker can guess the answers and set your password to something they know.
